In the post-genomics era, future breeding strategies rely on the investigation of abiotic stress tolerance responses and their correlation to genetic traits (
 Cramer, 2010; 
 Yang et al., 2012; 
 Dal Santo et al., 2016; 
 Fortes and Gallusci, 2017). Gene co-expression networks (GCN), based in the notion that genes involved in similar or related processes exhibit similar expression patterns under different experimental conditions, are the preferred strategy (
 Wong et al., 2013). To this respect, several online platforms have been developed for 
 V. vinifera (
 Table 1).
